# NETWORK::GET_USER_STARTER_ACCESS

## Returns
* **E_PREMIUM_PACK_TYPE**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Retrieves the type of pack, if any, which grants the user access to the starter pack content

Checks some commerce stuff
